{"tid":228782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"工程技能交換學習","createTime":"2017-05-04T07:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T05:02:28.000Z","uid":71160,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89c88924cc56addcabb4db10573c220e4853a6fe","tid":228782,"uid":71160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:00:13.000Z","msg":"各位巴打好<br />\n我開呢個post係想交換技能。<br />\n我自己本身係建造業議會學水喉（1年制），拎左水喉同消防中工。我覺得好多時候都係hea多過做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我打算用技能換技能，我想學電器、機械，如果你識既話又對水喉有興趣的過，tg我：nevergiveup17<br />\n另外，我都會總結返係cic學過既知識比返你聽。<br />\n<br />\n我簡單講下水喉中工點考： 要識睇圖同埋畫圖，鑽孔，打喉碼，量碼喉長度，安裝喉到配件上面，屈之字喉，砌水箱。<br />\n合格條件係：唔漏水，尺寸準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A: <br />\nQ1: 點解要搵你學而唔去建造議會學?跟cic學每個月仲有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nA: 因為跟cic學，讀佢個（水喉）成人班最快都要4個月先畢業，技能交換可以節省好多時間。 同埋你係cic報左一個course之後，要等一年後先再以報一個新course。講真，要由學到識做我覺我得根本唔洗四個月時間（起碼水喉係咁先），明白左點做之後練四五次出去考試一定無死，無錯係一定合格！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #yup一來# <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過跟cic學有師傅教你，二來會包曬你所有牌照（綠卡、安全卡、考試費）。不過缺點上面講左。<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 場地<br />\nA2: 新界火炭工廈（待定）<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 交換條件<br />\nA3: 起碼教授者對果項技能要有充份既認識，能清晰表達，有信心同耐性教好對方，並有能力解決到該技術既任何困難。"},{"pid":"859f72622adc660d2b761dc55c6ab2d65127c305","tid":228782,"uid":71160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"6eba553ed068ebd08b433f4616ba4a5c74f40322","tid":228782,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa40892529647419cf59439d547f1912688aa347","tid":228782,"uid":71160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電器 木工都識DD</blockquote><br />\n有無中工牌"},{"pid":"089ec5f025960e2198641b6073b7bda1f1260741","tid":228782,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:26:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"516ac0507b78855c47e5bd12e591cd7268033530","tid":228782,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/152634_7e00850a67853a5db36253e1bbeb23c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F152634_7e00850a67853a5db36253e1bbeb23c0.jpg&h=ada8eedb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/152707_5dbe36bf4d0c7b546e7329f0c1aae080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F152707_5dbe36bf4d0c7b546e7329f0c1aae080.jpg&h=37648bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上水cic"},{"pid":"d7a5d8b978c1c089f5a634a37143007914eff3d9","tid":228782,"uid":71160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"跟cic仲有個唔好，就你開始左個course, 讀讀下唔想讀既話，但又拎左佢d津貼的話呢，你要比返曬你拎過既所有津貼。同埋你考果d牌，佢要等你讀完成個course先比你"},{"pid":"0f444a34f35a0e165289226925f9526183146140","tid":228782,"uid":82974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"19 engine 留名<br />\n<br />\n咩技能都冇想學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab27019e61f37b5ea2d72c02936224b20795787","tid":228782,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:25:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>19 engine 留名<br />\n<br />\n咩技能都冇想學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTg: nevergiveup17"},{"pid":"2daae5b12382fa74a9c7311e2a069f77ec7a85a3","tid":228782,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xw67hU2